Class DataStoreConflictHandler.ConflictData<T extends Model>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.datastore.DataStoreConflictHandler.ConflictData<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the model instances that conflict (they are both of the same type.)
    Enclosing interface:
    DataStoreConflictHandler

    public static final class DataStoreConflictHandler.ConflictData<T extends Model>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a conflict between two models that has occurred during model synchronization. One was found locally, and another found in the remote system.
